## üõ† Configuration

Set in `.env`:

| Variable        | Description                                | Example             |
|-----------------|--------------------------------------------|---------------------|
| `GENAI_API_KEY` | Google Generative AI (Gemini) API key      | `sk-‚Ä¶`              |
| `GENAI_MODEL`   | Gemini model to use                        | `gemini-1.5-flash`  |

See `.env.example` for reference.
